Query.OnInit: rem Always set defined range of coding key _if corrvalue.CDmachinCodingKey.min NE 99200 force corrvalue.CDmachinCodingKey.min 99200 force corrvalue.CDmachinSpecType.min 992 _endif _if corrvalue.CDmachinCodingKey.min NE 133100 force corrvalue.CDmachinCodingKey.max 133100 force corrvalue.CDmachinSpecType.max 1331 _endif rem Build table with parameter key SELECT ParameterKey INTO MachineParameterKey FROM SalesTypeMapping WHERE CodingKey = $CDmachinCodingKey$ rem Build table machine specific type SELECT SpecificType INTO MachineSpecType FROM SalesTypeMapping WHERE CodingKey = $CDmachinCodingKey$ rem Build table TypeSeries SELECT TypeSeries INTO MachineTypeSeries FROM SalesTypeMapping WHERE CodingKey = $CDmachinCodingKey$ rem Build sales type table SELECT SalesType INTO MachineSalesType FROM SalesTypeMapping WHERE CodingKey = $CDmachinCodingKey$ rem Build machine class table SELECT Class INTO MachineClass FROM SalesTypeMapping WHERE CodingKey = $CDmachinCodingKey$ rem Set correctionvalues min and max on every startup _if CDmachinCodingKey EQ MDmachinCodingKey SELECT VarNameMin VarValueMin INTO TempParaMin FROM Parameter WHERE EXECUTE db_write_vars TempParaMin SELECT VarNameMax VarValueMax INTO TempParaMax FROM Parameter WHERE EXECUTE db_write_vars TempParaMax _endif rem When machine type was changed correction values will be set invalid _if CDmachinCodingKey NE MDmachinCodingKey force MDmachinCodingKey $CDmachinCodingKey$ force CDmachinSpecType $database.MachineSpecType.1.1$ force MDmachinSpecType $database.MachineSpecType.1.1$ rem Set correctionvalues min and max before writing values SELECT VarNameMin VarValueMin INTO TempParaMin FROM Parameter WHERE EXECUTE db_write_vars TempParaMin SELECT VarNameMax VarValueMax INTO TempParaMax FROM Parameter WHERE EXECUTE db_write_vars TempParaMax rem Set ALL correctionvalues when machinetype was changed SELECT VarName VarValue_$database.MachineParameterKey.1.1$ INTO TempParameter FROM Parameter WHERE EXECUTE db_write_vars TempParameter rem Set retains when machinetype was changed SELECT VarName VarValue_$database.MachineParameterKey.1.1$ INTO TempRetain FROM Retain WHERE EXECUTE db_write_vars TempRetain _endif rem Set correctionvalues base on every startup SELECT VarNameBase VarValue_$database.MachineParameterKey.1.1$ INTO TempParaBase FROM Parameter WHERE EXECUTE db_write_vars TempParaBase rem Set UNMODIFIABLE correctionvalues when boot.cnf has changed _if boot.cnf_filetime NE MDBootCnfFileTime force MDBootCnfFileTime $boot.cnf_filetime$ SELECT VarName VarValue_$database.MachineParameterKey.1.1$ INTO TempParaUnmod FROM Parameter WHERE VarAttribModif = 0 EXECUTE db_write_vars TempParaUnmod _endif
